N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 20.55 - Transportation credit on bulk unit pool milk

State Regulations

For pool milk received by a handler in a pool or partial
pool unit, a transportation credit at the rate of 15 cents per hundredweight
shall be computed. Notes
